title: How many number one hits did Dionne Warwick have? - Quora

response.answer_text: You have to be more definitive in your questions. There is the Billboard Hot 100, Billboard Adult Contemporary, Billboard R & B charts. Not to mention Cash box, Radio & Records and many more national charts. Then you have trade and Industry charts. Also during most of her era every city & radio station had their own charts. So just counting the above entities she had 368 number one songs. I did not include Duets or projects like We are the World!
